@node DWASO "Dwarven Soldier"

@{b}Dwarven Soldier@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = FE(C1/C1/C1)
Type    = Summon Dwarf (2/1)
Cost    = 1R
Artist  = Douglas Shuler / Rob Alexander / Randy Asplund-Faith

@{b}NOTE@{ub}: There are THREE different artworks for this card.

