Flavor Text: @{i}"Although the Dwarves staunchly defended their walled
              city-states against the Orcs, their civilization was
              the first to fall, and its name was sadly lost."
              --- Sarpadian Empires, vol. I@{ui}

Flavor Text: @{i}"Let no one say we did not fight until the last..."
              ---Headstone fragment from a mass grave
                 found in the Crimson Peaks@{ui}

Flavor Text: @{i}There is a legend among present-day Dwarves that the
             Dwarves of Sarpadia will one day return to defend
             Dwarvenkind against a deadly peril.@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_D.guide/DWSOL}

