Flavor Text: @{i}"I asked one of my aides how they do it, but all he'd
              say was, `Trust me, Mayor, you don't want to know.'"
              ---Lydia Wynforth, Mayor of Trokair@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_G.guide/GOCHI}

