@node GOBFL "Goblin Flotilla"

@{b}Goblin Flotilla@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = FE(U1)
Type    = Summon Goblins (2/2)
Cost    = 2R
Artist  = Tom Wanerstrand

Text(FE): Islandwalk
          At the beginning of the attack, pay <R> or any creatures
